text: Croatia Airlines is a government owned airline of Croatia. It flies to domestic and international destinations. Its main airport is Zagreb Airport. It's usual destinations are Dubrovnik, Split and Zadar.Flight International 3 April 2007 Since November 2004, the airline has been a member of Star Alliance.
